<br>
The idea of the summit is to bring the world's leaders together and discuss the future, primarily through making plans that promote sustainable development.<br>
<br>
What are your views on these summits? Are they very important meetings that should be taken very seriously, and not be relegated to page 5 of our newspapers. Or are they just a waste of time and money?<br>
